{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352540/extras/Picture1.png?t=1727976710\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sentience is an online multiplayer game where 2 teams of up to 4 players wrestle for control of society long after the humans they were built to replace have disappeared.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Blend in as a Rogue</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your intelligence and blend in with the AI as a Rogue to avoid detection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352540/extras/32434a06-d888-45a5-8256-abe6843c0894.gif?t=1727976710\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Sentinels are Watching</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Assert control as the Sentinels tasked with catching Rogues and preventing anything, or anyone, from deviating.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352540/extras/9424d646-94ef-46c7-82bb-489eda5be257.gif?t=1727976710\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Do What it Takes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your abilities and perks for detecting a sentient Rogue or escaping a Sentinel's clutches. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352540/extras/2d127ba1-9a14-4a79-a8a6-4a7bcf66eb55.gif?t=1727976710\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customize your Bot</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spend your hard-earned bolts and processors to customize your robots with unique cosmetics. Change your hat, head, torso and legs to create your ideal robot. Use the \u2018Chicken Dance\u2019 taunt as a Rogue to tease a nearby Sentinel or use a \u2018Jazz Hands\u2019 finisher to show off your Sentinel skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352540/extras/f8decf07-126e-40ff-9247-4f893ecdc7a5.gif?t=1727976710\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play across 6 stunning, dystopic levels that have lasted long after the last humans disappeared.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352540/extras/5c0d07aa-3157-474a-b192-7bc4d46fb9b5.png?t=1727976710\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Play as either Sentinel (hunters) or Rogue (hunted)</strong> - each with unique abilities and playstyles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiplayer round-based cooperative gameplay</strong> - Play individually or as a team with up to 4 friends online.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Free-to-play</strong> - With upgradeable cosmetic features including animations, costumes and consumables.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Leaderboards</strong> - Compete to become the best a-round.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Progression and daily rewards</strong>  - Be rewarded for playing daily and unlock new items as you progress.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Replayable Missions</strong> - Hack terminals or deliver armed crates as a Rogue to escape the patrolling Sentinels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fun Game Modes</strong> - For an extra challenge complete your side goal to earn extra XP. Remember to stay charged in Energy Drain mode.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sentience offers a unique take on the beloved stealth multiplayer genre with its sci-fi dystopian setting. It\u2019s free-to-play so give it a try today! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Join our discord to find folks to play with and keep up to date on all things Sentience!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352540/extras/d32419b9-6f4a-4983-9a16-fc10e16d8c90.png?t=1727976710\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"On a Roll","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352540/04991aa42b7ab4254398839e66ad1a14a253a256.jpg"},{"name":"Pro Player","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352540/6ace12f64057f31471c161c86a17b2cfaa2092d0.jpg"},{"name":"Hungry","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352540/65a88aaaf9a98a79eb39414ddd41e2d5770a6b2c.jpg"},{"name":"Time with Friends","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352540/d58f1ea151f0bc7fd7a9381524bd32f14ac07fdc.jpg"},{"name":"Moving up in the World","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352540/40ac0a809828df7326cc4ae5a2180a0e05ba28bb.jpg"},{"name":"A Whole 'Nother Level","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352540/8e7a69a48c1be39023fdf1b998c6e20ca2aebda2.jpg"},{"name":"Mastered","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352540/14cdbd312b897b185125a2c46aaff7249bf7f9eb.jpg"},{"name":"Grand Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352540/f9f77bc05fd81599c70d53b627720c69e2fc2ace.jpg"},{"name":"Freedom","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1352540/8732430b15f2e26698dfb7ba27ddba5da144cdc6.jpg"},{"name":"Escape Artist","path":"